  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-6 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Seven factors are fully assessed with achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels; six factors are marked not-applicable with thorough rationale documenting why each falls outside the scope of this V&V 40 assessment. Decision: Accepted on the basis of complete and satisfactory evidence across all in-scope credibility factors.",
